title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: In this small patch of open field, most of the earth has been tilled except for a small section, a grassy path that leads over to a large dunking booth.  A banner is held aloft over the path and reads, "Afraid to get wet?!  Come take your turn in the booth!"
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, south, west, northwest
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
